thread.title: More Pre-K Seats Planned for Upper East Side

author: Leslie Brody
title: More Pre-K Seats Planned for Upper East Side

locations.name: upper east side new york city

text:
New York City officials are adding more than 400 public prekindergarten seats on the Upper East Side after parents complained for years that demand far outstripped supply.
